      "role": "user",
      "content": "but therapy feels like such a joke. like, how am i supposed to \"move forward\" when the person who made my life worth living is just... gone? it's not just sadness, it's like a part of me was ripped out. there's no \"healing\" from that. it just feels like i'm a shell of a person forced to keep performing these daily routines that mean absolutely nothing without him.",
